---
title: "analyze-frontend — Preflight → Detect → Orientation → two-wave analysis → persist JSON → report"
---
%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Claude
    participant FS as File System
    participant FD as frontend-detector<br/>subagent (gating)
    participant TSP as tech-stack-profiler<br/>subagent (Wave 1)
    participant Wave2 as Wave 2 — 7 specialist<br/>subagents (parallel,<br/>stack-informed):<br/>framework-idiom-extractor,<br/>design-system-scanner,<br/>component-inventory,<br/>data-flow-mapper,<br/>architecture-analyzer,<br/>feature-flow-detector

    User->>Claude: /analyze-frontend [frontend-path] [--only <area>]

    note over Claude: Capture start timestamp
    Claude->>Claude: START_TS = date +%s<br/>RUN_TS = date -u +%Y%m%dT%H%M%SZ<br/>DISPLAY_TS = date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Preflight
    Claude->>FS: Check cwd for .claude/ directory
    FS-->>Claude: present / absent
    alt .claude/ absent
        Claude->>User: No .claude/ found — run /init-project first
        break Skill aborts
            Claude->>User: Aborted
        end
    end

    note over Claude,FD: Phase: Detect frontends (cheap — no user interaction)
    Claude->>FD: Invoke with {project_root, user_hint_path}
    Note right of FD: Scans for package.json + framework<br/>manifest (vite.config.*, next.config.*,<br/>angular.json, svelte.config.*, etc.).<br/>Returns flat list.
    FD-->>Claude: {frontend_roots: [{path, framework, entry_points}]}
    alt No frontends detected
        Claude->>User: No frontend roots found. Skill aborts.
        break Skill aborts
            Claude->>User: Nothing to analyze
        end
    end

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Orientation (single user checkpoint)
    Claude->>FS: Read .claude/state/frontend-analysis.json<br/>(schema_version, generated.ts, plugin_version,<br/>frontends_analyzed, only_filter)
    FS-->>Claude: JSON or absent
    Claude->>FS: Glob existing artefacts + get ages:<br/>.claude/docs/reference-component-creation-template*.md<br/>.claude/rules/frontend-design-system*.md<br/>.claude/rules/frontend-components*.md<br/>.claude/docs/reference-architecture-frontend*.md<br/>.claude/docs/reference-component-inventory*.md<br/>.claude/sequences/frontend-data-flow*.mmd<br/>.claude/sequences/features/*.mmd
    FS-->>Claude: file list + ages

    Claude->>User: Detected frontends: N roots (framework)<br/>Existing analysis: <date> · plugin <ver><br/>Artefacts: <name> <age ✓/⚠/✗> ...<br/>Numbered menu:<br/>[1] Full — all frontends, all areas<br/>[2] Full — only <main root><br/>[3] Refresh stale — --only <area>  (if stale exists)<br/>[4] Custom --only / subset of roots<br/>[5] Skip — go to /create-frontend-docs
    User-->>Claude: number / custom filter
    alt skip
        Claude->>User: Analysis is current.<br/>Run /create-frontend-docs or /update-frontend-docs <area>.
        break Skill aborts — nothing to do
            Claude->>User: Aborted
        end
    end

    note over Claude,TSP: Phase: Wave 1 — Stack profile (per frontend, serial)

    par For each confirmed frontend root
        Claude->>TSP: Invoke tech-stack-profiler with<br/>{frontend_root, project_root,<br/>framework_hint, entry_points}
        TSP-->>Claude: {stack_profile: framework+version,<br/>bundler, language, ts_strictness,<br/>styling_model, class_naming,<br/>state_libs[], routing, data_fetching,<br/>rendering_mode}
    end

    note over Claude,Wave2: Phase: Wave 2 — Deep per-axis analysis (parallel, stack-informed)
    Claude->>Claude: TodoWrite — create checklist before fan-out:<br/>☐ framework-idiom-extractor<br/>☐ design-system-scanner<br/>☐ component-inventory<br/>☐ data-flow-mapper<br/>☐ architecture-analyzer<br/>☐ feature-flow-detector

    par For each {frontend_root, specialist} pair — concurrent
        Claude->>Wave2: Invoke one specialist with<br/>{frontend_root, project_root,<br/>stack_profile (from Wave 1),<br/>entry_points, style_rules_path,<br/>target_file_shape}
        Wave2-->>Claude: {summary_row (YAML),<br/>artefact_body (markdown)}<br/>or sentinel SKIP if N/A
        Claude->>Claude: TodoUpdate — ☑ <specialist-name>
    end

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Persist structured analysis
    Claude->>Claude: Merge Wave 1 + Wave 2 into JSON schema 1.1<br/>(full overwrite if no --only; merge if --only)
    Claude->>FS: Write .claude/state/frontend-analysis.json
    FS-->>Claude: OK

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Report
    Claude->>Claude: END_TS = date +%s<br/>wall_clock_sec = END_TS - START_TS
    Claude->>FS: Write .claude/state/reports/<br/>analyze-frontend-DISPLAY_TS.md<br/>(per rules/report-format.md)
    FS-->>Claude: Report saved

    Claude->>User: Dashboard:<br/>Frontends analyzed · Stack per root<br/>JSON ✓ .claude/state/frontend-analysis.json<br/>Duration · Report path<br/>Next: /create-frontend-docs
